Description :
        Hatoko’s getting sick and tired of being pushed around by her childhood friend and professional model, Subaru (a.k.a. The Sadistic Prince). One day Subaru drags her along to... a photo studio!? Filling in for a model, she is forced to play the role of Subaru’s girlfriend. Amid the confusion, Subaru tells her he loves her as his face gets closer to hers...
